room_title: Escape room "Brain Freeze" by Holmes Escape Games in Houston
room_description: A local legend surrounds the Brain Freeze Ice Cream Shoppe. Brain Freeze was the spot to hang, but now remains frightfully empty except for the owner Mr. Giggles, known for the creepy clown costume he wears to greet potential...customers. It's said the Giggles likes to put his best customers on ice! Can you find the evidence and escape Brain Freeze before Mr. Giggles returns or are you destined to become his next customer??
